{
  "stem": "14737.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It is true that in some communities, there were more anti-Semitism for a simple reason because in the churches, the priests, even they were lenient.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they were preaching that the Jews killed Christ.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, the little boy who was 10 or 11 years old heard this in the church, Jews killed Christ.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So probably this was the basis of being them somehow anti-Semite to a Jew, because the Jew killed him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That's how it went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But nothing-- for no other reason were they anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "As I said, but the more intelligent who were living there and who were like, from Hungary, Hungarians, so they were [INAUDIBLE] warned, they were somehow anti-Semites, but secretly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "During the Czech regime was no anti-Semites in that sense.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Jews occupied themselves mostly with some trade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Some were small, little farmers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there a few who had there some business, but not talking about-- grocery business, but not necessarily like today's supermarkets, had stores for basic necessities in town, like kerosene, and soap, or needles, for basic things.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, religious observance-- religious observance, actually, almost in the whole Carpathian, people were all the religions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no such a thing as non-religious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everyone not to go to a synagogue, who heard that they counted them, they knew exactly who goes, and almost every one.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But was nothing else to be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the only place like, we'll say, for entertainment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not-- they didn't go for entertainment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it is the only place for-- where they went for-- to, to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a rabbi, a very distinguished man by the name of Usher Zelig Greenshwieg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was an old man, but one of the most great scholars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But his-- he distinguished himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
